{"parse":{"title":"Why We Sleep","pageid":55333944,"revid":858534803,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\">Not to be confused with <a href=\"/wiki/Why_We_Nap\" title=\"Why We Nap\">Why We Nap</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox vcard\" style=\"width:22em\"><caption style=\"font-style:italic;padding-bottom:0.2em;\">Why We Sleep: The New Science of Sleep and Dreams <span class=\"Z3988\" title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Why+We+Sleep%3A+The+New+Science+of+Sleep+and+Dreams&amp;rft.author=%5B%5BMatthew+Walker+%28scientist%29%7CMatthew+Walker%5D%5D&amp;rft.pages=368\"></span></caption><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/File:Why_We_Sleep_book_cover.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Why We Sleep book cover.png\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/94/Why_We_Sleep_book_cover.png/220px-Why_We_Sleep_book_cover.png\" width=\"220\" height=\"339\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/9/94/Why_We_Sleep_book_cover.png 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"254\" data-file-height=\"391\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Author</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Matthew_Walker_(scientist)\" title=\"Matthew Walker (scientist)\">Matthew Walker</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Language</th><td>\nEnglish</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Genre</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Science_book\" title=\"Science book\">Science book</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Published</th><td>\n3 October 2017, <a href=\"/wiki/Penguin_Random_House\" title=\"Penguin Random House\">Penguin Random House</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Pages</th><td>\n368</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a></th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-241-26906-0\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-241-26906-0\">978-0-241-26906-0</a> (Hardcover)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>Why We Sleep: The New Science of Sleep and Dreams</b></i> is a <a href=\"/wiki/Science_book\" title=\"Science book\">science book</a> about <a href=\"/wiki/Sleep\" title=\"Sleep\">sleep</a> by the <a href=\"/wiki/Neuroscience\" title=\"Neuroscience\">neuroscientist</a> and \"sleep scientist\" <a href=\"/wiki/Matthew_Walker_(scientist)\" title=\"Matthew Walker (scientist)\">Matthew Walker</a>. Walker is a Professor of Neuroscience and Psychology and the director of the Center for Human Sleep Science at the <a href=\"/wiki/University_of_California,_Berkeley\" title=\"University of California, Berkeley\">University of California, Berkeley</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Walker spent four years writing the book,<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> in which he argues that <a href=\"/wiki/Sleep_deprivation\" title=\"Sleep deprivation\">sleep deprivation</a> is linked to numerous fatal diseases, including <a href=\"/wiki/Dementia\" title=\"Dementia\">dementia</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Why_We_Sleep&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Cooke, Rachel (2017-09-24). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2017/sep/24/why-lack-of-sleep-health-worst-enemy-matthew-walker-why-we-sleep\">\"The shorter your sleep, the shorter your life: the new sleep science\"</a>. <i>The Observer</i>. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number\" title=\"International Standard Serial Number\">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.worldcat.org/issn/0029-7712\">0029-7712</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2017-09-24</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Observer&amp;rft.atitle=The+shorter+your+sleep%2C+the+shorter+your+life%3A+the+new+sleep+science&amp;rft.date=2017-09-24&amp;rft.issn=0029-7712&amp;rft.aulast=Cooke&amp;rft.aufirst=Rachel&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Flifeandstyle%2F2017%2Fsep%2F24%2Fwhy-lack-of-sleep-health-worst-enemy-matthew-walker-why-we-sleep&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWhy+We+Sleep\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Gray, Richard. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.bbc.com/capital/story/20170911-are-you-a-sleep-procrastinator\">\"Are you a sleep procrastinator?\"</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2017-09-24</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Are+you+a+sleep+procrastinator%3F&amp;rft.aulast=Gray&amp;rft.aufirst=Richard&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fcapital%2Fstory%2F20170911-are-you-a-sleep-procrastinator&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWhy+We+Sleep\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\"